Package sanctuary

Interface Housing

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HousingUnit
    public interface Housing
    Housing interface represents the housing units present in Jungle Sanctuary. Jungle Sanctuary consists of multiple isolations and enclosures. Different monkeys are assigned housing IDs and sometimes are transferred based on multiple factors.
